DT_PASSWORD     Allows you to retrieve or change users password

                msg->Command = 101
                msg->Data    = 1 or 0

                if msg->Data = 1, then msg->String will be the password.
                if msg->Data = 0, then the password will be msg->String.
(FUNCTION #: 101 )

@endnode
