DT_LOCATION     Allows you to retrieve or change users location

                msg->Command = 102
                msg->Data    = 1 or 0

                if msg->Data = 1, then msg->String will be the location
                if msg->Data = 0, then the location will be msg->String
(FUNCTION #: 102 )

@endnode
